About Us

Trusafe Security & Solutions Pvt. Ltd. is one of the fastest- growing security agencies based in Moradabad, Uttar
Pradesh.
We are committed to offering reliable, professional, and trained manpower for all your security needs
residential to industrial sectors.
With verified guards, proper uniforms, and 24/7 monitoring, your safety is in trusted hands.

Our Services

Providing top-notch security solutions for residential areas, society premises, banquet halls, events, hospitals, factories, commercial spaces, schools, and colleges.

Trained Guards

Our security guards are highly trained professionals equipped to handle all security challenges with expertise and vigilance.

Customized Plans

24/7 Surveillance

Offering round-the-clock surveillance and monitoring services to guarantee the safety and security of your premises day and night.

Why Choose Us?

Trusafe offers PSARA Licensed guards, verified and uniformed. With regular monitoring by field officers, we ensure a professional look and discipline. Benefit from affordable rates and flexible contracts.
